;                        GET INFO ABOUT PB’S PCRE VERSION                       
;                      and print it in a GFM Markdown table                     
;{==============================================================================
;                       — by Tristano Ajmone (@tajmone) —                       
; ==============================================================================
; PureBASIC 5.50 | "Get_PCRE_Info.pb" v1.0 (2016/12/09)
; https://github.com/tajmone/purebasic-archives
